K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-1: a'arya sarba dharma n'a tri ka n'a ma dh'a ra ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-3: 'phags pa chos thams cad kyi yum zhes bya ba'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phag 'tshal lo /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-7: bcom ldan 'das mnyan yod na bzhugs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' po la bka' stsal pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-10: khyod kyis chos thams cad kyi yum zhes bya ba'i phyag rgya'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-11: nad thams cad rtu zhi bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-12: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsungs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-13: nga yang da ltar 'chad pa zungs shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-23: sarba dharm'a: p'a sha pa nyee sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-24: de nas gnas gtsang ma'i lha rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-26: bdag cag gis kyang 'di'i snying po brjod par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330a-29: aa na le ae lu pha aa lu phe murta aa mugte /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330b-0: sarba dharma aa @330b dhi ba ti ya pradta /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330b-2: aa dhi ga ta dzny'a ne /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330b-4: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas tshe dang ldan ba kun dga' po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330b-5: thams cad dang ldan ba'i 'khor de dag yid rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon po par bstod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-060:330b-6: chos thams cad kyi yum zhes bya ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
